        dc:description           "Figure 1. SEM (A–E, G, H) and optical (F) micrographs of Leptodorosida zherikhini gen. nov., sp. nov., Ust’- Baley, Asian Russia. (A) Holotype, PIN 1873/106; (B) paratype, general view, PIN 1873/102; (C) antenna II, PIN 1873/101; (D, E) antenna II, PIN 1873/115; (F) antenna II, PIN 1873/123; (G) head and thoracic limbs, PIN 1873/107; (H) thoracic limbs, PIN 1873/116. Scale bars: 1 mm (A, B); 0.1 mm (C–H)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4669492/files/figure.png" .

