        dc:description           "Figure 6. Optical (A, B) and SEM (C–H) micrographs of Smirnoυidaphnia testacea, Novospasskoe, Asian Russia. (A) Holotype, PIN 3000/40; (B) antenna II, PIN 3000/46; (C) PIN 3000/1, general view; (D) its mandibles and antenna II; (E) its postabdominal claws; (G, H) PIN 3000/015, general view and resting eggs. Scale bars: 1 mm (A, C, G); 0.1 mm (B, D–F, H)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4669502/files/figure.png" .

